   - Applied `sqlgen::full_join<Product, "p">` to perform FULL JOIN with Product table using alias "p"
   - Defined join condition using `"s"."supplier_id"_t1 == "p"."supplier_id"_t2` to match supplier IDs
   - Used table alias literals (`_t1`, `_t2`) from `sqlgen::literals` namespace

